Project Description
Simple Note XML makes it easier for ASP.NET Developers to build lists. You'll no longer have to write things down. It's developed in ASP.NET 2.0 C#.

SimpleNoteXML is not able to be defined at this moment, but it's fully self-contained black box of functionality.
